{"tid":1511322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[核彈] 冇開會 唔告得「進入或逗留在會議廳範圍」","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:11:04.000Z","uid":95138,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6784e02ad5d7bb7c7dd665fc5a3fb417e96ed356","tid":1511322,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"根據立法會權力及特權條例，會議廳範圍嘅定義係咁嘅：<br />\n<br />\n會議廳範圍(precincts of the Chamber) 指會議廳及立法會辦事 處及毗鄰的旁聽席以及供公眾人士與報界、電視台及電 台的代表使用或用以容納他們的地方，而除主席根據第 (2) 款作出例外規定者外，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">在立法會或任何委員會舉行會 議當日全部時間</span></strong>，此詞亦包括會議廳所座落的整座建築 物，以及為立法會而使用或提供的任何與該建築物毗鄰 或屬於它的前院、庭院、花園、圍場或空地; ( 由 1994 年第 11號第 3條修訂;由 2000年第 71號第 3條修訂 )<br />\n<br />\n簡單D講，如果立法會個日有會開，咁個棟建築物先算係會議廳範圍<br />\n<br />\n而睇番立法會網站，當日係冇會開嘅<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">2019年7月1日沒有公開或閉門會議</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n換言之，政府唔可以用哩條告手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1634cf00acb35793175adb4255996198421381","tid":1511322,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67e612bfcb4a82b4c375e40e5b90477424f904c3","tid":1511322,"uid":97078,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"驊驊話ok就ok"},{"pid":"0db6cf0cd02e4b9ca368265f66b7191d08b0bbc9","tid":1511322,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"手足應該唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c91c70c134ef9189e77bcd40b8ebefa956fc127","tid":1511322,"uid":124711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"根本政治檢控 重有一班紅官"},{"pid":"f76e617f830a3b9a263b5b7eec4b71525e711de7","tid":151132